Name: scramble

Info

C program to scramble and unscramble your files. DO NOT USE FOR
SENSITIVE FILES, USE REAL ENCRYPTION!

Usage

compile: make all
use: ./scramble <file> <hex number>
example: ./scramble secret.txt abad1dea

Notes

Again: USE REAL ENCRYPTION!
<hex number> must be an even number of hex digits.
Not tested with more than 8 hex digits.
If file given has been previously scrambled, the program should
produce the original file if the correct hex number is given.

